                Sir R. Acland
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-0ae71688-e39e-4d54-afce-28f25fc10596" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-04-06/debates/0f1f2dec-d34b-4de5-a83f-f6f9d272fa96/31AmendmentOfLaw#contribution-0ae71688-e39e-4d54-afce-28f25fc10596">
