                Mr. Scollan  (Renfrew, Western)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-666d542e-edbd-4873-9d33-bf8c2b6082ac" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
